{"id":19506,"date":"2019-11-10T09:43:49","date_gmt":"2019-11-10T02:43:49","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=19506"},"modified":"2020-03-20T21:21:59","modified_gmt":"2020-03-20T14:21:59","slug":"cach-tao-landing-page-mien-phi-gutenberg","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/cach-tao-landing-page-mien-phi-gutenberg","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o landing page b\u1eb1ng Gutenberg mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><strong><em>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t landing page b\u1eb1ng Gutenberg mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/em><\/strong> trong nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng trang \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Page Builder plugin \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i cho WordPress.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Page builder \u0111\u00f4i khi s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 th\u1eeba khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 mong mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o nhanh m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i trang \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n cho blog.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh d\u00f9ng &#8220;\u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c b\u1eafn ru\u1ed3i&#8221; b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lu\u00f4n tr\u00ecnh so\u1ea1n th\u1ea3o Gutenberg c\u1ee7a WordPress \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf <a href=\"\/design\/landing-page-la-gi\/\">landing page<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y l\u00e0:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e0i c\u00e1c plugin page builder qu\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 cho website.<\/li><li>Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o trang trong WordPress.<\/li><li>Trang t\u1ea1o b\u1eb1ng Gutenberg c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 load SI\u00caU T\u1ed0T so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c Page Builder.<\/li><li>Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Gutenberg v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t&#8230; tr\u00ecnh so\u1ea1n th\u1ea3o<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft th\u00ec Gutenberg l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00ecnh so\u1ea1n th\u1ea3o editor ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Wordpress t\u1eeb phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 5.0 (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/news\/2018\/12\/bebo\/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress &#8220;Bebo&#8221; 5.0<\/a> tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra m\u1eaft th\u00ec r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia r\u1ea5t quan ng\u1ea1i Gutenberg s\u1ebd \u0111oe d\u1ecda c\u00e1c Page Builder Plugin khi ra m\u1eaft. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y, Gutenberg c\u0169ng v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t editor v\u00e0 c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp c\u00e1c page builder \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Gutenberg b\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn ra khi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o trang:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Kh\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/strong>. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 thao t\u00e1c k\u00e9o th\u1ea3, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u1edf frontend (b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o \u1edf backend WordPress)<\/li><li><strong>Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 giao di\u1ec7n di \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/strong>. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho b\u1ea1n t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh hay xem tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf giao di\u1ec7n di \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, giao di\u1ec7n di \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i c\u1ef1c quan tr\u1ecdng hi\u1ec7n nay.<\/li><li><strong>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eabu t\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n<\/strong>. Trong khi c\u00e1c page builder lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap d\u00f9ng tham kh\u1ea3o hay t\u1ea1o nhanh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang trong 5 ph\u00fat.<\/li><li><strong>T\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/strong>. C\u00e1c Gutenberg block \u0111a ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n n\u00ean b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Layout, Section, ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n kh\u00e1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Slide, Pop-up, Form,&#8230;<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Gutenberg c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng so v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c Page Builder kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 T\u1ed0C \u0110\u1ed8 front end.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng trang qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, th\u00ec d\u00f9ng Gutenberg t\u1ea1o trang s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t landing page \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi Gutenberg mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m, n\u00ean b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t plugin b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 (Gutenberg Add-on) \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Gutenberg.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 Qubely plugin (Free).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">B\u01b0\u1edbc #1: C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Qubely mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"8gtJIxUFyv\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/qubely\/\">Gutenberg Blocks and Page Builder \u2013 Qubely<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Gutenberg Blocks and Page Builder \u2013 Qubely&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/qubely\/embed\/#?secret=8gtJIxUFyv\" data-secret=\"8gtJIxUFyv\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"\/out\/qubely\" data-eafl-id=\"22392\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">Qubely<\/a> s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Gutenberg b\u1eb1ng b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng h\u1eefu \u00edch nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>T\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh Responsive (t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh giao di\u1ec7n di \u0111\u1ed9ng)<\/li><li>T\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Section<\/li><li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ed9ng (animated)<\/li><li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng chia trang (section divide)<\/li><li>M\u1eabu t\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n (tempalte)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn <a href=\"\/out\/qubelypro\" data-eafl-id=\"22509\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">Qubely Pro<\/a>?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft<\/strong>, Qubely mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o trang \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng Qubely block \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n hay t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e2ng cao h\u01a1n cho c\u1ea3 vi\u1ebft blog (Gutenbeg d\u00f9ng cho vi\u1ebft blog l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh) th\u00ec h\u00e3y xem x\u00e9t. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">B\u01b0\u1edbc #2: C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh &#8220;nh\u1eb9&#8221; cho WordPress Page tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd Page Attribute, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Qubely th\u00ec t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng Qubely s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra th\u00eam 2 lo\u1ea1i Page Attribute cho WordPress.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Qubely Full Width<\/strong>. T\u1ea1o trang v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng to\u00e0n trang v\u00e0 c\u00f3 header hay footer c\u1ee7a theme.<\/li><li><strong>Qubely Canvas<\/strong>. T\u1ea1o trang v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a theo tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh c\u1ee7a Qubely v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 header hay footer.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 theme WordPress c\u0169ng s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n 2 Page Attribute \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Default template<\/strong>. Chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng trang th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch post tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y.<\/li><li><strong>Page Builder (theme)<\/strong>. Chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng trang s\u1ebd tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p theo Page Builder v\u00e0 Theme \u0111ang d\u00f9ng. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 theme s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Page Attribute n\u00e0y.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 cho b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n t\u00f4i, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y xem \u1ea3nh minh ho\u1ea1 b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Default-Template-layout.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"455\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Default-Template-layout-1024x455.png\" alt=\"Default Template Layout\" class=\"wp-image-22523\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Default-Template-layout-1024x455.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Default-Template-layout-218x97.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Default-Template-layout-300x133.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Default-Template-layout-700x311.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Default-Template-layout-768x341.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Default-Template-layout.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Default template<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"457\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Page-Builder-cua-theme-1024x457.png\" alt=\"Page Builder Cua Theme\" class=\"wp-image-22524\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Page-Builder-cua-theme-1024x457.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Page-Builder-cua-theme-218x97.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Page-Builder-cua-theme-300x134.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Page-Builder-cua-theme-700x312.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Page-Builder-cua-theme-768x342.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Page-Builder-cua-theme.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Page Builder (theme) (c\u00f3 header v\u00e0 footer)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"457\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Fullwidth-atribute-1024x457.png\" alt=\"Qubely Fullwidth Atribute\" class=\"wp-image-22525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Fullwidth-atribute-1024x457.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Fullwidth-atribute-218x97.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Fullwidth-atribute-300x134.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Fullwidth-atribute-700x312.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Fullwidth-atribute-768x343.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Fullwidth-atribute.png 1919w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Qubely Full Width (c\u00f3 header v\u00e0 footer)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"444\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Canvas-1024x444.png\" alt=\"Qubely Canvas\" class=\"wp-image-22526\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Canvas-1024x444.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Canvas-218x95.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Canvas-300x130.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Canvas-700x304.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Canvas-768x333.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Qubely-Canvas.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Qubely Canvas (kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 header v\u00e0 footer)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1eady t\u00f3m l\u1ea1i b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn Page Attribute n\u00e0o?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110a s\u1ed1 theme n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c Page Builder plugin nh\u01b0 <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Astra (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/astratheme\/\" target=\"_blank\">Astra<\/a> hay <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Suki (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/sukitheme\/\" target=\"_blank\">Suki<\/a> (ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c theme th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1) th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn Page Builder (theme) attribute, b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u00e1c tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh cho header nh\u01b0 Transparent Header, Sticky Header,&#8230;s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Qubely v\u00e0 c\u0169ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed7i x\u1ea3y ra.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng theme kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 <strong>Page Builder (theme)<\/strong>, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn <strong>Qubely Full Width<\/strong> thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Chon-Page-Atributes.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"534\" height=\"521\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Chon-Page-Atributes.png\" alt=\"Chon Page Atributes\" class=\"wp-image-22504\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Chon-Page-Atributes.png 534w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Chon-Page-Atributes-218x213.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Chon-Page-Atributes-300x293.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Ch\u1ecdn Page Builder (theme) n\u1ebfu c\u00f3<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">B\u01b0\u1edbc #3: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1o landing page v\u1edbi Qubely Gutenberg<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c Page Builder kh\u00e1c, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u khi t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t trang m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n<\/strong>. Qubely Gutenberg cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n IMPORT m\u1eabu t\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n v\u1edbi th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n m\u1eabu t\u00edch h\u1ee3p bao g\u1ed3m t\u1eebng section v\u00e0 to\u00e0n trang. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i th\u00edch l\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n IMPORT c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh ho\u1ea1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00eam v\u00e0o media c\u1ee7a WordPress (C\u00e1c Page Builder kh\u00e1c t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng sideload lu\u00f4n \u1ea3nh v\u00e0o media c\u1ee7a WordPress v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian xo\u00e1 n\u00f3).<\/li><li><strong>B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi trang tr\u1eafng<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo \u00fd th\u00edch s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ghi nh\u1edb l\u00e0 ROW block \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 section. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c Gutenberg block ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eb1m trong v\u00f9ng ch\u1ee9a ROW block.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Trang-tao-san-trong-Qubely.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"484\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Trang-tao-san-trong-Qubely-1024x484.png\" alt=\"Trang Tao San Trong Qubely\" class=\"wp-image-22531\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Trang-tao-san-trong-Qubely-1024x484.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Trang-tao-san-trong-Qubely-218x103.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Trang-tao-san-trong-Qubely-300x142.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Trang-tao-san-trong-Qubely-700x331.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Trang-tao-san-trong-Qubely-768x363.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Trang-tao-san-trong-Qubely.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e1c trang m\u1eabu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n (Starter Pack)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Section-tao-san-trong-Qubely.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"484\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Section-tao-san-trong-Qubely-1024x484.png\" alt=\"Section Tao San Trong Qubely\" class=\"wp-image-22532\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Section-tao-san-trong-Qubely-1024x484.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Section-tao-san-trong-Qubely-218x103.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Section-tao-san-trong-Qubely-300x142.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Section-tao-san-trong-Qubely-700x331.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Section-tao-san-trong-Qubely-768x363.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Section-tao-san-trong-Qubely.png 1499w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption><em>C\u00e1c Section m\u1eabu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n (Sections)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Row block<\/strong> l\u00e0 block c\u1ef1c quan tr\u1ecdng khi b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf trang b\u1eb1ng Qubely Gutenberg b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t giao di\u1ec7n di \u0111\u1ed9ng (Reponsive), t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eebng section v\u1edbi nhau, t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng separate divide, t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec7m v\u00e0&#8230; Fullwidth.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Row-block-trong-Qubely.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"565\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Row-block-trong-Qubely.png\" alt=\"Row Block Trong Qubely\" class=\"wp-image-22545\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Row-block-trong-Qubely.png 565w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Row-block-trong-Qubely-218x232.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Row-block-trong-Qubely-283x300.png 283w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 565px) 100vw, 565px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Row Block (Qubely)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/luon-chon-full-width-row-block.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"473\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/luon-chon-full-width-row-block-1024x473.png\" alt=\"Luon Chon Full Width Row Block\" class=\"wp-image-22534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/luon-chon-full-width-row-block-1024x473.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/luon-chon-full-width-row-block-218x101.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/luon-chon-full-width-row-block-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/luon-chon-full-width-row-block-700x323.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/luon-chon-full-width-row-block-768x354.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/luon-chon-full-width-row-block.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Lu\u00f4n ch\u1ecdn FULLWIDTH \u1edf Block ROW (Qubely)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen th\u00eam block v\u00e0o trang theo tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y t\u1eeb tr\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng. G\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng r\u1ed1i m\u1eaft, kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec7m (padding) hay l\u1ec1 (margin). D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 giao di\u1ec7n di \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Co-Row-block-va-khong-co-Row-block.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"474\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Co-Row-block-va-khong-co-Row-block-1024x474.png\" alt=\"Co Row Block Va Khong Co Row Block\" class=\"wp-image-22536\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Co-Row-block-va-khong-co-Row-block-1024x474.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Co-Row-block-va-khong-co-Row-block-218x101.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Co-Row-block-va-khong-co-Row-block-300x139.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Co-Row-block-va-khong-co-Row-block-700x324.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Co-Row-block-va-khong-co-Row-block-768x356.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Co-Row-block-va-khong-co-Row-block.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf v\u00e0o Row Block b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec7m padding, margin, content position,&#8230;<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Quy t\u1eafc n\u1eb1m l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi Page Builder v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Qubely Gutenberg l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n nh\u00f3m c\u00e1c block (hay element) v\u00e0o t\u1eebng section ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Giao-dien-di-dong.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"471\" height=\"727\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Giao-dien-di-dong.png\" alt=\"Giao Dien Di Dong\" class=\"wp-image-22544\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Giao-dien-di-dong.png 471w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Giao-dien-di-dong-218x336.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Giao-dien-di-dong-194x300.png 194w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Giao-dien-di-dong-454x700.png 454w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb trang tr\u00ean di \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng (Responsive)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>Nh\u1edb b\u1ecf block \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb &#8220;count&#8221; m\u1ed9t block element v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1eafng tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o xong trang.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi Gutenberg gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c Page Builder qu\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh sau th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Elementor, <a href=\"\/out\/beaverbuilder\" data-eafl-id=\"22447\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">Beaver Builder<\/a>, <a href=\"\/out\/brizypro\" data-eafl-id=\"22391\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">Brizy<\/a>, <a href=\"\/out\/thrivearchitect\" data-eafl-id=\"22840\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">Thrive Architect<\/a> hay <a href=\"\/out\/divi\" data-eafl-id=\"23164\" class=\"eafl-link eafl-link-text eafl-link-cloaked\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\">Divi<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u1eefng trang \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o b\u1eb1ng Gutenberg c\u0169ng s\u1ebd KH\u00d4NG g\u00e2y xung \u0111\u1ed9t m\u1ed9t khi b\u1ea1n c\u00e0i \